title: The Offspring - Hellfest 2024
overview: Come Out and Play, All I Want, Want You Bad, Staring at the Sun, Make It All Right, In the Hall of the Mountain King (Edvard Grieg cover) (with "Smoke on the Water" and "Iron Man" riffs as intro), Blitzkrieg Bop, (Ramones cover), Hammerhead, Bad Habit, Gotta Get Away, Drum Solo, Why Don't You Get a Job?, Pretty Fly (for a White Guy), The Kids Aren't Alright  Encore: You're Gonna Go Far, Kid, Self Esteem
